te-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_17\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 17\">Chapter 17</a>, Jon IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings: Daeron I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\">13.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-1\">13.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_13\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 13\">Chapter 13</a>, The Soiled Knight.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_F